<p>Dreaming of milking a cow indicates great wealth and other interpretations that we will explain for single, married, pregnant and divorced men, such as milking milk or buffalo milk or goat milk - seeing the milking cow for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> and others. On:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a cow dream</span></h2>
<p>Milking cows or <strong>milking cows in a dream</strong> is an indication of sufficient sustenance; because milk in interpretation indicates money or benefits, whoever dreams that he milks his cow, he achieves good and money in that year.</p>
<p>Referring to the interpretation of seeing a cow being milked or any type of animal in a dream, this indicates good companionship, flattery, policy, earning a living and appreciating milking.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
