</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever dreams that he milks a cow and drinks her milk, becomes rich if he is poor, trustworthy and high, and if he is rich, his wealth and dignity increase.<br/>Whoever sees that he is milking a cow and does not drink her milk, this indicates that he collects a lot of money but does not profit from it.</p>
<p>Whoever dreams that he <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-حلب-جمل-في-المنام?page=621" > milks a camel </a> has obtained money from his master, for milking is blood contaminated with unlawful money, and milking is cunning.<br/>Milking camels is work in the land of the Arabs, and milking the blessed is work in the land of non-Arabs. Milking her blood, then she betrays the ruler in his authority, and if the milking is poison, then she reaps unlawful money, and the camel and drinking from her milk, marries the righteous, and if he is married, he will have a son. A blessing is born to him and God Almighty</p>
<p>Milking the cow: If you dream that you are milking a cow, this indicates great opportunities that have been presented to you, but you have not yet taken advantage of them.  Otherwise, the dream may mean that you are being milked or exploited by others<br/>Milking cows If you dream that you are milking and the milk is abundant in its rush from the udder, and the cow is hot and hot, then this means that many opportunities will escape you, but you will soon win.<br/>Whoever dreams that he milks blood and blood comes out of his udder, it is interpreted as a violation of the king, even if it is a dream.<br/>Referring to the interpretation of seeing a cow being milked or any type of animal in a dream, this indicates good companionship, flattery, policy, and earning a living.<br/>If a person sees milk flowing from the ground, it will be unfair to the people of that place</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
