</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Some interpreters believe that milking a cow in a dream is a sign of exploitation or a symbol of greed and avarice.. And some of them did not like the interpretation of the dream, especially if the dreamer or the dreamer was not the one who milked the cow in the dream.</p>
<p>It is hated in interpretation to see the sleeper in his dream as someone else other than him milking his cow, especially if there is enmity, competition or disagreement between them, this dream may indicate loss resulting from such enmity, and the vision may indicate the following:  A serious and disgusting violation that the dreamer is subjected to by his enemies, envy and haters.  ...</p>
<p>The interpreters also disliked seeing a friend milking his friend's cow, because such visions express greed, stinginess, and the exploitation of that friend by his friend...</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
