</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span><span></span></p>
<p>It is also unpleasant in interpretation to see the sleeper as a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-شخص-غريب-في-المنام?page=754" > stranger </a> milking a familiar cow in a dream.  Such dreams may express bad luck, harm or plague that may befall the owner of this cow while he is awake.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>It is also disliked in dream interpretation and expressing vision to see a dead person milking a cow or drinking her milk... If the cow is unknown, this indicates a year full of worries, troubles and hardships.  ... And if it is known, it is malice or harm or loss that may befall its owner.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
