</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a milking cow in a dream</span></h2>
<p>It is a good year full of livelihoods and good news.  The milking cow also indicates the presence of a generous woman and often symbolizes in men's dreams their wives, as well as indicating the pregnancy of a married woman.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever dreams that he has a milking cow in his house, then prosperity, blessings and blessings will come to that house and in that year.  Whoever asked for food and saw in his dream that a milking cow entered his house or grazed in a place full of grass, this is a very good interpretation, because the milking cow in this context is a clear symbol that indicates good arrival.  To the king, good that is in accordance with his desire, and often the milking cow, like a fat cow, carries a woman.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
