</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>In interpretation, it is also pleasure for those in distress, hardship or distress... All colors are praiseworthy in milking cows, but the black cow is one of the most symbolic in dream interpretations that express news and prosperity.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever dreams that he milks a cow until he sees it producing a lot of milk, this is in interpretation a benefit or <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > a lot of money </a> that the dreamer enjoys in that year.</p>
<p><span></span><span></span></p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
