</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a cow dream for a man</span></h2>
<p>Whoever dreams of men as if he is holding the udder of a milking cow and starts milking it until he sees milk flowing from it, and he has collected this milk in a pot or a pot or a bucket... This is in interpretation by money that he collects it or acquires it by the dreamer as a result of hard work and diligence... and the interpretation came to the milk poured into a container, it indicates money that is preserved or preserved or collected.</p>
<p>As for the man who sees in a dream that he is milking a cow and does not see her milk flowing, this indicates that the wife is barren and may not give birth... and the vision may indicate the man's own sterility... If he sees that the milk spills or spills on the ground, then he could not collect it in his dream, and in waking life he wastes his money and wastes his livelihood and what his right hand earns from expenses or high payments.  from religion.. And perhaps the wasting of the collected milk indicates wasting time on things that are not useful or do not benefit.  This scene often also indicates chasing desires and pleasures, and abandoning work and worship</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a cow dream for a single woman</span></h2>
<p>We have indicated in many places on this blog (Dream Interpretation website) that a cow in a dream indicates a year.  As we mentioned - based on <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> - that milk comes down with money, as well as indicating instinct and faith, and it is praiseworthy for whoever saw it as if he drank it, and it is praiseworthy for whoever saw it.  As if they were giving her to drink, the cow is known or known, in the interpretation of the woman.  She may have been referring to her mother.  If the unmarried woman sees that she is milking that cow, then she benefits from her mother or from any other woman she knows.</p>
<p><span></span></p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
