</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>If the cow in the dream of the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-غير-المتزوجة-لابن-سيرين?page=786" > unmarried woman </a> is unknown (and she does not know her owner), then she is in interpretation a good year, if this cow is fat or her udder is full of milk.</p>
<p>If the dreamer is a student or a student and she sees herself milking this cow, then this dream indicates a successful year... provided that she sees the milk being collected in a clean container or bucket...</p>
<p>But if she sees the milk spilling to no avail on the ground or grass, then the vision in this regard indicates a waste of time and effort.  It can also indicate failure and failure.  Therefore, the owner of the vision should compensate for what she lacks and double her efforts in order to achieve academic success in that year.</p>
